name: When'sthenextNewJerseyPATHtrain
0:
”Alexa, ask PATH Schedule whats next from Newark to World Trade Center”
”Alexa, ask PATH Schedule when is the next train from Journal Square to 33rd Street”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: path schedule
des: This skill is for New Jersey PATH customers. Ask Alexa when the next train is and she'll happily tell you the next two times. Currently the skill only works with outbound trains from Journal Square to 33rd Street -- in the future outbound and inbound train schedules will be added, as well as the ability to select the route and discern between weekday, weekend, and holiday schedules.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
